Let $u,v$ be sequences in $\K^{\mathbb N}$, then $
(N,D)\in\Ann_\RecI (u,v)$
if and only if $(aN,aD)\in\Ann_\RecI(u,v)$ for all $a\in\RecI^\times$.
\end{lemma}

